<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="on-purpose">on purpose</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-deliberately">1.<strong>故意地；有意地 (deliberately)</strong></h4>
<p>反 by accident： </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Cinderella left her shoe on the stairs on purpose.
灰姑娘故意把自己的鞋落在楼梯上。</p><footer> 2014 福建</footer></div></div>